name: Sysbrix Leather
description: Our company is engaged in Manufacturing
overview:
Incepted in the year 2007, at Delhi (India), we, “Sysbrix Leathers Pvt Ltd”, are known as the most prominent Manufacturer and Supplier of a comprehensive assortment of Men Leather Belts, Men Leather Wallets, Ladies Leather Wallets, etc. The products offered by us are fabricated using premium quality factor inputs and advanced technology in accordance with the set international standards. These are widely praised among our prestigious clients for their durable finish, tear & water resistance, fine finish and attractive design.

Infrastructure: We have constructed a well-established infrastructural facility that is equipped with the latest machinery and equipment, which enables us in meeting bulk & urgent orders of customers. This contemporary set-up assists us in handling the diverse and bulk fabrication processes of high quality leather products.

Our Quality Assurance: We give our utmost attention to the quality of the products and offer elevated quality range of products to our customers. To ensure the quality of our products, we use only high grade raw material for the manufacturing process. All our products are designed as per the international quality standards. Apart from quality, we also give utmost importance to timely delivery of the product assortment at clients’ end.

Client Satisfaction: Being a customer conscious firm, we believe in offering clients with quality products thereby maximizing their satisfaction and trust in us. We have adopted some policies for the clients that include cost effective pricing structure, timely delivery, quality assurance and transparent dealings. We also offer our valuable customer’s easy modes of payment with high reaction as counter back for the feedback we receive. Moreover, we are highly appreciated for our ethical business policies, transparent dealings, client friendly policies and efficient transportation system.

Our Products: Men Leather Belts, Men Leather Wallets, Ladies Leather Wallets, etc.
